3.0.6 - 21st February 2016
    * Policies are isolated from each-other by being wrapped in braces.
	* Additional test-case coverage to validate the above.

3.0.5 - 18th April 2015
    * Add "App::Slaughter" module to claim the CPAN namespace.

3.0.4 - 28th October 2014
    * Prevent multiple simultaneous runs.

3.0.3 - 24th October 2014
    * Updated MANIFEST to be current.
	* Updated POD for many modules.

3.0.2 - 23rd October 2014
    * Significant POD fixes and updates.
	* Minor changes to Slaughter::Private module to make it a real module.
	* Added LICENSE
	* Added version number in our modules.

3.0.1 - 19th October 2014
	* Fail cleanly if the transport isn't loaded.
	* Removed sample Apache module.
	* Minor POD updates to fix warnings/errors.
	* Add Mojo::UserAgent as explicit dependency.

3.0.0 - 18th October 2014
	* Initial upload to CPAN.
